{"tid":492170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★bitcoin終於被hack--挖礦平台被黑客攻擊 錢包內比特幣數量變成 0","createTime":"2017-12-07T09:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T13:48:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"bd53638e6857f21d988d2d05e54ee08d5355bc54","tid":492170,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"虛擬貨幣 Bitcoin 比特幣在本日升到 14173 美元高位，本來令人興奮，但對於一部份採礦人士來說，就好比從天堂跌入地獄。大型雲端挖礦平台 NiceHash 被黑客攻擊，在最新聲明中，承認 NiceHash Bitcoin wallet 的內容被盜，有關網站停止所有服務以調查事件。根據網路資料，這批涉及今次偷竊案的比特幣的總額，達到 6,200 萬美元（約港幣 4.84 億元）。<br />\n<br />\n根據社交平台與官方網站的消息，在香港時間（下同）12月6日早上11時，NiceHash 服務全面停機，在同日下午 4 時官方發出報告，指服務正進行維修。<span style=\"color: red;\">有網民發現自己的帳戶被提空，錢包內的比特幣數量變成 0</span>，社交媒體上因此流傳 NiceHash 被黑客入侵的消息。<br />\n<br />\n到了 12 月 7 日凌晨 4 時，NiceHash 終於發出用戶最不想看到的報告，就是宣佈「NiceHash Bitcoin wallet 的資料被盜」，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/12/07/nicehashstolen/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2Fnicehashstolen%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8314e243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/12/07/nicehashstolen/fun-tech/</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"8148c3537b29ec6afd4ec9b7be25751e7475884c","tid":492170,"uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4d7ea9ea908c19f32b794f47bc0b7e2f342d60","tid":492170,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2017-12-07-16.00.06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%