 />\n你咪用 bitcoin 買野囉, 今日對 $11k 美金聽日對 $13k, 你今日比 bitcoin 定聽日?<br />\n貨幣係用黎交易. 浮動到咁重只會不停減小. 用 Bitcoin 出糧呀? 今個月出 0.05 bitcoin 下個月 0.05 = 加人工? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係商品多過一切, 重要係非世界性. 你去敘利亞用 Bitcoin 買野囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金屬無可代替 (唔係紙金), 成個 Bitcoin back by 成班相信 Bitcoin 既人. <br />\n家下係雞棚第二期, 好多專家教人買 Bitcoin 甚至有期貨, 所以推到個波勁大. 真正識玩既係自己出 Coin, 襯 D 人未醒就快手推多 D 麥樂雞, 麥樂鴨, 麥當雞, 當當鴨 Cap 水."},{"pid":"cb7214014f00a1bde91bc18947459c7b3d5d0fd1","tid":492170,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"Hero<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46336ab9c0f0656049c2cd4e9b2e680adc6352a6","tid":492170,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"大驚小怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f6b21530a9e8fd93a0ed3d9fbcb0ca865fc6c2","tid":492170,"uid":54390,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"係個挖礦平台比人hack, 唔係bitcon比人hack"},{"pid":"9d36725ed03e24331488a96273fa7a08ac011888","tid":492170,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"molamola"},{"pid":"273b673063ebc75192f0c8a49e8f3dceb8c8f4a8","tid":492170,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"NSA 啲 algorithms 有 backdoor 講咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7244a803cd824608e338153b997c4757fd51c20e","tid":492170,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:36:33.000Z",